Invocation Name: helix rock radio
des: Welcome to Helix Rock Radio your home for online rock and talk radio. Helix Rock Radio is the brainchild of Brandon as a way to have a great radio station to listen to all the time. Brandon, an avid audiophile, podcaster, streamer, and radio guy, wanted to mesh music and podcasting into one making Helix Rock Radio. The mission of Helix Rock Radio is to bring genuine and great rock radio online in a different way. The station will be a lively entertaining mix of chat and rock music of the last fifty years. And, of course, we’ll have plenty of fun. We will forge relationships with the listeners and provide a trusted friend and an engaging and entertaining platform for all. Our mission at Helix Rock Radio Suffolk is to be that radio station that provides you with the best quality music and talk radio online.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
